Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.37,0:00:07.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:13.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I made reservations for Fukurai University's\NJapanese cultural research group...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:12.01,Dialogue6,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\pos(362,54)}{\i1}GOLDENTIME{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.01,0:00:16.97,Dialogue5,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(239,286)}Return to Yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.11,0:00:26.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, if we could meet in a dream, could I say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:51.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Say, if sadness alone floats down from the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:59.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If that kind of voice pains you even now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.65,0:01:03.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if, off to the side, our hands are placed on each other's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:07.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This memory wouldn't fade, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:15.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if, when our eyes meet, I can't say the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:19.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your words illuminate the world more than anyone else's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:23.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Next to me, "Goodbye means I love you," you say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.78,0:01:25.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be forthright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.41,0:01:27.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Though I alone sing of loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:29.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't smile
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.35,0:01:31.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you means I'm in love with you," you say
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:36.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The world's end of love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.51,0:01:52.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:53.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:56.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's already here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.88,0:01:58.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.11,0:01:58.98,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.65,0:02:00.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.82,0:02:01.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.32,0:02:03.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.49,0:02:04.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:08.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.46,0:02:10.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you looking at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.66,0:02:15.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come over here, Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:19.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.80,0:02:23.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're hanging up these lights before the fourth years arrive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:26.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about these lanterns.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:32.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,N-no! You're scaring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.08,0:02:32.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:34.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We're not scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:36.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.35,0:02:37.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:40.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing weird about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't get to go on our overnight trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:45.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but let's have fun today to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:48.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The president's connections got us this place, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.23,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:52.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right? Isn't this fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:54.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The festival club is so much fun, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:06.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've really, really missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:09.75,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What have you been up to lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:13.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well... lately... I... just, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.05,0:03:14.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Just..."?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.59,0:03:17.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can't help that, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:25.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say we see you and Roboko as... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.27,0:03:28.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sort of like a fertilized egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.24,0:03:30.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.97,0:03:33.37,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Two life forms have become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:35.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:41.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you and Roboko were always one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.65,0:03:45.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're the genes that will carry our souls on to the next generation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:46.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:49.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.72,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is Linda-senpai not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.89,0:03:52.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:56.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'd come here from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:03:57.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But forget about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.17,0:04:00.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, she went home to Shizuoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:03.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk about it right after I told you to forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.17,0:04:08.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:11.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I really don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.78,0:04:13.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What I'm trying to say is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:22.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We all want to include you and Roboko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.02,0:04:23.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You get it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.50,0:04:31.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's that! Get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:34.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, just because you broke up with Roboko,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:42.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,neither of you should quit the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:43.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.81,0:04:45.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:50.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We've been calling and texting Roboko lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:52.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but we can't get in touch with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.82,0:04:54.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we called you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:57.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,when we asked about Roboko, you gave vague answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:59.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what it means?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.89,0:05:01.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:02.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:07.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're not a couple anymore, that doesn't mean your bond with us is lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right, guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:10.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We'll soothe the pain of lost love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's cheer up Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.38,0:05:17.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:17.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.31,0:05:19.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:20.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.32,0:05:21.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}No, no, no!\N{\c&H1BFEF9&}Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.18,0:05:23.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Why would you assume that?\N{\c&H1BFEF9&}Tada! Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.19,0:05:29.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Tada! Banri!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:25.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Kouko and I are...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.36,0:05:32.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Roboko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:34.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Roboko's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.33,0:05:38.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Roboko's returned from the heart repair factory!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:42.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give a warm welcome to the nearly broken Roboko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Roboko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.91,0:05:44.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.94,0:05:46.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.54,0:05:49.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that! You've got the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.11,0:05:50.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, you don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:55.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't break up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We wasted our time trying to be nice to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:06.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We were really worried about what we'd do if you quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:08.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.56,0:06:09.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.53,0:06:13.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, don't blame them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.74,0:06:15.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not their fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're the one who's most at fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:23.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You were the first to assume they broke up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:27.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You guys said you were sure about it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:29.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to blame us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:32.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for jumping to conclusions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:32.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}We might have come dangerously close to it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:34.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't close at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't even within the range of "close."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:40.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.09,0:06:41.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.56,0:06:43.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought you look good in your yukata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.66,0:06:46.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This? I made it this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.63,0:06:52.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I decided I would go and see fireworks with you this summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:54.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It rained the other day, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:55.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:57.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.91,0:06:59.41,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just got word.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:04.19,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(148,96)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Mind if I come to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:04.19,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(146,126)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}today's fireworks
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:04.19,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(147,157)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}extravaganza?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:04.19,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(146,186)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}It's okay, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:04.19,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(147,216)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.31,0:07:04.19,Dialogue4,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(147,247)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:07:04.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Former president Hoshino-senpai is coming here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:06.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Hosshi-san's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.42,0:07:09.19,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wouldn't come if he couldn't find a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:10.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:11.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He found work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:13.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:15.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He'd been looking really gloomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's celebrate with everything we have!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:18.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:26.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hosshi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.81,0:07:33.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Your legendary pirouette is so cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.78,0:07:35.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it? Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this place is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.49,0:07:41.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We should have helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.86,0:07:43.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:45.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hosshi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:47.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on your employment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:50.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:50.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:53.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now all the fourth years have found jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.80,0:07:54.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.84,0:07:55.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:58.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.41,0:08:01.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:06.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't actually found a job yet... you might say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:14.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted a change of pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.92,0:08:18.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:21.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:22.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:24.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's this mood in the air?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.90,0:08:31.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:34.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys out there in the world are lousy judges of character!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.51,0:08:35.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:39.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, drink more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.54,0:08:39.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}In any case, I'm glad you're all okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:41.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oka-chan's injury is better now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:46.09,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.39,0:08:47.86,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:50.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I was at home, I felt so uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.43,0:08:53.83,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, how did you hear about the accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.10,0:08:56.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you know. From people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:01.20,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:03.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was worried until I finally saw you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:08.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It was worth coming back just to see you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:21.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:22.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.12,0:09:28.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did we ever light fireworks together before I lost my memory?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:40.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You were in the same class for all three years of high school, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:41.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Before I fell off that bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:46.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You were both on the track team, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:49.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You must've looked so cool, Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,About those fireworks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:56.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at your left leg, Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:57.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My left leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:02.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's a burn scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:07.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In the summer of our second year, when we lit fireworks on the track team's overnight trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:10.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,a bottle rocket fell over and struck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.64,0:10:12.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.01,0:10:13.07,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:17.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I hurt myself protecting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.11,0:10:18.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This scar is a badge of honor!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.81,0:10:20.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:27.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I ran away quickly, but you were stupidly slow to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.32,0:10:30.62,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We got in a lot of trouble with our adviser afterward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:34.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.66,0:10:35.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's all in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.80,0:10:39.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Banri...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:42.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going home for summer break?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:44.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:46.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,My parents have been pushing me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:51.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.55,0:10:54.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you happen to see Banri while you're back home,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.42,0:10:56.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll hang out with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.02,0:10:57.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.55,0:11:03.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I wasn't going to bring this up, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:06.65,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,...can I say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.03,0:11:13.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A high school class reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:14.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:17.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Our class is holding a reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.34,0:11:24.40,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure you wouldn't want to come, so I wasn't going to tell you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.01,0:11:26.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to stop by?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.28,0:11:30.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I won't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:35.25,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's just... everyone's worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:38.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If you show them you're fine,\NI think they'll be really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:41.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to tell you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.90,0:11:44.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.93,0:11:46.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri will attend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.90,0:11:47.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You will, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:51.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What? You won't?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.04,0:11:53.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You will, right? Of course you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:02.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to the class reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:10.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do something I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:12.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for making the decision for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:16.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Did I cause you trouble again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.30,0:12:17.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.67,0:12:21.00,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to stop running from my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:22.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:26.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:30.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The person everyone wants to see is the\NTada Banri from before I lost my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:34.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He's a completely different person from who I am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:40.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When they see me, they might think, "Who is this guy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.52,0:12:43.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"You're not the one we want to see."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.12,0:12:46.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"We want to see the old Banri."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:48.49,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,They might think something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:54.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You told me the other day that I abandoned my friends and family and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.64,0:12:57.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:13:00.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:03.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know you don't remember them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:04.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.85,0:13:06.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.22,0:13:11.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It helped me decide to face my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.05,0:13:16.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go see my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help what they think about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.29,0:13:23.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'll apologize for making them worry, and thank them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:27.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.33,0:13:31.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'll finally get to see the whole Banri.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The whole me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:38.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I think I couldn't really accept you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:43.21,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I only saw the Banri I wanted to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:51.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't accept that there were people who knew a Banri that I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:56.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I must have been jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:13:59.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But, what you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:03.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll do my best, so you do your best, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:05.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"Don't get out of the car."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:10.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When you said that, I realized I loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:15.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I realized it was fine for me to keep loving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:20.39,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I love you because you're you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.39,0:14:23.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy that you're whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:29.55,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if there are sides of you\NI don't know, or don't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.96,0:14:32.30,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,If that's who you are, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:36.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're whole, that's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:42.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm struggling because\NI've lost sight of my whole self.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:47.74,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's part of who you are, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:52.22,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So go see your past with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:59.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,See for yourself the Banri you've forgotten, who you were before you met me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.59,0:15:02.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and then tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.92,0:15:26.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Can I open this box?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.16,0:15:31.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but could you take that box to the corner over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.49,0:15:34.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's full of fragile stuff, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:36.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're a real slave driver, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.26,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:43.27,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san, you're staying here tonight, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:43.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take until nighttime to finish putting things away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.77,0:15:49.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're going to make me work until then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.64,0:15:51.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:53.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that why you came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:55.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.38,0:15:59.45,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I had no intention of helping you move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I was a little curious, so I came to take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:04.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard your apartment wasn't what you imagined,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.06,0:16:05.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd come laugh at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:07.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why you brought an apron?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:11.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, let's get this done quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.03,0:16:14.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be the first one to stay over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.90,0:16:16.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not staying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:18.54,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not! Not even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stay over even if the world ends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.98,0:16:26.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:31.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to guess what you're thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:34.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:36.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking about Banri, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.02,0:16:39.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're wondering what he's up to in Shizuoka right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:43.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:47.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Once you fall in love, you really love that person through thick and thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:50.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't everyone like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:53.17,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.17,0:16:56.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I have a lot of respect for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:16:57.24,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:17:00.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:05.35,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're just pretending to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.25,0:17:08.38,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:14.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai, you're not leaving yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:17.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm staying until the first train.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.46,0:17:19.99,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Once the trains start running,\NI'll get on a bullet train.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.87,0:17:23.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're going home again?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.87,0:17:26.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I meant to head right back home in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:30.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but I was suddenly asked to work here, and that delayed my plans a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.87,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I got to see the two underclassmen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:37.28,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Did I do something I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:40.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I made you worry by telling you about the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.96,0:17:44.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:45.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:47.43,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.10,0:17:51.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um, do you need some help?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.93,0:17:53.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:54.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:59.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Um... how long are you going to be at home?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.94,0:18:02.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Until the end of summer break, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a class reunion,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:06.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,and I have plans to hang out with some friends after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:08.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,A reunion, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:10.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:13.15,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have any plans like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.15,0:18:14.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,None yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.92,0:18:17.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri's gone home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:19.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,With fewer friends around, I don't have much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:23.10,Dialogue3,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(430,166)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Shizuoka
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:23.10,Dialogue3,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(299,215)}{\c&HFFFFFF&}Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.83,0:18:22.93,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Linda-senpai, you're from Shizuoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:24.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.97,0:18:28.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri said he's from Shizuoka, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:31.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you'll run into Banri somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.94,0:18:33.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That won't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.81,0:18:35.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuoka's a big place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:38.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.85,0:18:39.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:40.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.85,0:18:41.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.82,0:18:42.85,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.61,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.72,0:18:47.31,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I'm doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.79,0:18:55.16,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I'm going back to my apartment first.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:55.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:01.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Three is fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but make them all different flavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:06.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:08.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,And where's the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.64,0:19:09.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.91,0:19:17.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad Kaga-san's feeling better.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:20.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could have seen Oka-chan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:24.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:27.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,She said she's not done unpacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.32,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.43,0:19:30.56,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:32.06,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is something bothering you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:34.70,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say it's bothering me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:39.34,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Banri's from Shizuoka, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:41.51,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what high school he attended?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.51,0:19:42.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:45.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You know he doesn't really talk about his past.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:47.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.58,0:19:51.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he doesn't want to remember because of his accident before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.95,0:19:52.89,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:54.79,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You mean the one the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.79,0:19:55.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,No, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.76,0:19:56.69,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.69,0:19:58.36,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't heard, Yana-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:20:00.52,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,About when Banri fell from a bridge and got badly hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:02.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Badly hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.60,0:20:07.33,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,We were tricked by some weird cult and taken to their campsite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Banri told us about it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:12.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He fell from a bridge and was hospitalized for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:18.05,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, he said, "I'm interested in religion because I've had that experience."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.05,0:20:21.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,"No one else is interested, so let them go."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.91,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really true, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:27.29,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was a lie, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.29,0:20:32.12,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed he made something up so we could escape, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:36.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,When we went to the beach the other day, I saw a faint scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:37.73,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.60,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended not to notice,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:44.13,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,but maybe what he said at that camp was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:46.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,He said a bunch of other things, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.84,0:20:48.18,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, other things?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:52.04,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I don't know how much is true and how much is false.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.75,0:20:53.78,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:57.68,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,we shouldn't look into it too much if he doesn't want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:20:58.88,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:06.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,These look delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Take whichever one you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:09.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,It's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.96,0:21:11.76,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Since I made you guys worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.64,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're so big-hearted, Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:15.44,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:17.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying about my nice body?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.80,0:21:18.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kidding, I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:19.94,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're very thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:21.81,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Kouko, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.11,0:21:23.71,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.71,0:21:25.01,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,That Banri was hospitalized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.35,0:21:27.14,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yana-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.45,0:21:28.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.82,0:21:29.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:32.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.58,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Here, take a spoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.85,0:21:35.82,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:36.95,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You, too, Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.86,0:21:40.46,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll dig in, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:41.66,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:45.47,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. Kaga-san, how was Oka-chan's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.47,0:21:46.53,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You stayed over, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.53,0:21:47.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.63,0:21:50.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, she even made me help her move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:53.97,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You, doing work? Sounds cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:54.96,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.83,0:22:15.02,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, I'm telling you you're wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.33,0:22:18.50,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, you still don't notice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.50,0:22:24.84,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Though I've wanted to touch that arm for the past two or three hours
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.84,0:22:27.90,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I do not need forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.18,0:22:31.08,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe forever love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:38.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,The urge to scream is so great that, look, I can't stand it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.42,0:22:44.59,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,So why, why won't you notice even a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:51.80,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really, really in love with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:57.57,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need words of flattery
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.80,0:23:00.77,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Love me semi-eternally
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.07,0:23:04.11,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,After 5,000 years or so, I won't be interested
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:07.67,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not endless
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:10.92,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,I will die someday
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.08,0:23:17.42,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,Being told "I'll love you forever" won't make me happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.59,0:23:21.03,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,First, think only that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.33,0:23:25.63,Dialogue1,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,You'll love me till I die
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.93,0:23:40.95,Dialogue5,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(55,413)}My Hometown
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:29.74,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(289,357)}I want a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.74,0:23:30.77,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(309,357)}It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.77,0:23:33.91,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(116,357)}You'll find a job before Jack Frost arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.91,0:23:34.51,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(326,359)}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:35.98,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(190,362)}You'll be fine, Hosshi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.98,0:23:37.98,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(171,362)}Hey there, future prime minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.98,0:23:39.45,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(261,361)}Jack Frost, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:41.04,Dialogue2,Unknown,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\pos(233,359)}I wonder if he'll come.
